\title{Closed monoidal category}
\taxon{definition}
\import{macros}
\meta{external}{https://ncatlab.org/nlab/show/closed+monoidal+category}

\p{A [monoidal category](math-0021) #{(\cat{C}, I, \otimes)} is \em{closed} if for each #{Y \in \cat{C}} the [endofunctor](math-002F) #{-\otimes Y} has a [right adjoint](math-0028), #{[Y, -]}.}

\p{I.e. there is a [natural hom-isomorphism](math-0032) #{\Hom_\cat{C}(X \otimes Y, Z)\cong \Hom_\cat{C}(X, [Y,Z])}.}

